data.description: COME VIEW this 3 Bedroom home that offers a Bedroom, full bath, and laundry, all on the FIRST FLOOR.  Large Kitchen, Dining Room, and a Large Living Room.  PLUS, an office for personal work space. Checkout the deck on the back of the house that is perfect for BBQ'ing and lounging.  ALL of this sits on 1.03 acres.  Being sold AS IS.  Close to trails and lots of outdoor adventures.  Approximately 35 minutes to Bangor on State Rt 1A.
